sa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with their inhabitants, was as entire and per-</div><div class="t m1315 x57 h2d y2a02 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">petual as if the fires had been always burning-</div><div class="t m92 x57 h2d y2aa5 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the consumption was absolute and enduring-</div><div class="t m7d8 x57 h2d y2a80 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sinners were wholly cut off, and the cities </div><div class="t mab x57 h2d y2423 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forever rendered desolate; and (2) that in its </div><div class="t m3c3 x57 h2d y2331 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nature and duration this was a striking em-</div><div class="t m391 x57 h2d y2189 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blem of the destruction which will come upon </div><div class="t m158d x57 h2d y1f10 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the ungodly.&quot; And the apostle Peter ex-</div><div class="t m596 x57 h2d yd35 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pressly declares that God made Sodom and </div><div class="t m526 x57 h2d y1526 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gomorrah &quot;an ensample unto those that </div><div class="t m7bb x57 h2d y1e4d ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">after should live ungodly.&quot; 2 Peter 2 : 6. </div><div class="t m2ad5 xbe h6c y15e0 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I..ESSC_)1N </div><div class="t m2de8 x1b4 h4a y128b ff6 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">March 31, 1888. </div><div class="t me0a x8d h6c y116f ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUGGESTIONS FOR QUARTERLY </div><div class="t m964 x160 h6c y13f3 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">REVIEW. </div><div class="t m9a1 xa9 h2d y1384 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. WHY should God receive homage from </div><div class="t m2bf x57 h2d y20a9 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">all creatures ? </div><div class="t m127 xa9 h2d y1fd6 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mcb xb1 h2d y109b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What distinguishes the one true God </div><div class="t m117f x57 h2d y136b ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from false gods ? </div><div class="t m2b6 xa9 h2d y15d0 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1cd xb